- `GET /api/questions` ‚Äî returns MCQ questions + voice questions as JSON
- `POST /api/score/mcq` ‚Äî accepts `{answers: [], correct: []}`, returns MCQ score
- `POST /api/score/speech` ‚Äî accepts audio file (webm/wav), transcribes + scores, returns `{transcript, grammar, confidence, speed}`

